image.alt:
A probability tree. We will be naming paths
through the tree with the notation "{first branch-off: probability of branch-off; second branch-off:
probability of branch-off; ...}". Here is the tree:
        {S: 0.001 (red), D: 0.80 (red)};
        {S: 0.001 (red), not D: 0.20};
        {not S: 0.999, D: 0.16 (red)};
        {not S: 0.999, not D: 0.84};

Here is the probability tree with paths through the tree shown in "{
1st branch-off: probability of 1st branch off, 2nd branch-off: probability of 2nd branch off}":
            {H: 0.03, W: 0.98};
            {H: 0.03, not W: 0.02};
            {not H: 0.97, W: 0.01};
            {not H: 0.97, not W: 0.99};
